{"tid":1439614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再推罷課！ 請中學生學生會籌備罷課！","createTime":"2019-08-10T07:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T15:27:03.000Z","uid":20126,"like":59,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"89fdc0100b5d20581a1cf7ac1ec1dc5251f7ede9","tid":1439614,"uid":20126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:15:19.000Z","msg":"係依家比較膠着嘅狀態 我地make到比較大嘅noise就係中學生罷課<br />\n可能你會質疑 中學生罷課 邊有可能啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但幾星期前 又有邊個認為公務員集會 85全民罷工有可能？<br />\n今次運動中有不少中學生參與 罷課行動將會一呼百應！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">現在只欠一個<span style=\"color: violet;\">帶頭者</span></span><br />\n只要一間學生組織主動發起罷課 其他學校嘅學生組織必然響應！<br />\n<br />\n我在此建議 學生組織可先<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">定立一底線</span></span><br />\n如果港共政府係限期內不作有意義回應<br />\n學生將於9月2日起 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無限期罷課</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n無限期罷工對不少打工仔黎講有顧慮<br />\n但無限期罷課對學生顧慮較小<br />\n港共政權亦不得再無恥地迴避<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時間無多，開學日將至，籌備罷課需時<br />\n我在此懇求各中學學生會盡快籌備罷課</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncredit to:<br />\n真.罷課，係接下來最大既武器，決定運動成敗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434604\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434604</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果全香港中學生、大專生，真係在9月發起罷課，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講到明，唔搞掂五大訴求，一定唔會返學</span></span>，將會對香港政府構成超大既威脅。<br />\n<br />\n呢個可能係打開眼前樽頸位，最有效既方法。<span style=\"color: blue;\">今日已經係8月9日，如果要籌備，依家就要開始，要大規模的話，就要中學生組織、中學學生會、大專學生會，全力去籌備，大人配合搞「罷課不罷學」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫手推，開始第一波既預備先。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">今次罷課係只許成功，不許失敗，係我地眼前唯一既轉機！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93a533c2b3fafbeb95b9223bf07ee8c953f8997","tid":1439614,"uid":20126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:16:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3fc526310744f65e4338a43da47df27b1cb7f1c4","tid":1439614,"uid":20126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:16:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c93c5df857eba6bdff60c6752afd8247f3fdb448","tid":1439614,"uid":20126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:16:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ad568b1baa52eb286d63e53d4bd9f0e0a8e15b73","tid":1439614,"uid":20126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:17:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b93418b2a0ea5f913e0a5ae247d21493fa86eed2","tid":1439614,"uid":20126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:17:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"292ffa9d32c8200071e0d943fc1b447934075604","tid":1439614,"uid":20126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:17:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5766f5749f57be0c04dda7f29e86b9338b6f9f1d","tid":1439614,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90a1150b95ee695c5703f0d20d81807b3a2e60d","tid":1439614,"uid":224829,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:17:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7a4ed2b09e8aa56e634cca92e932b47b4fb71c4","tid":1439614,"uid":171149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:18:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"46978aa3a704ad0d47ef08c910fa0139beacfa18","tid":1439614,"uid":20126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f90a1150b95ee695c5703f0d20d81807b3a2e60d","tid":1439614,"uid":224829,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:17:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:18:25.000Z","msg":"一定要搞得成！ 對抗無賴政權"},{"pid":"eb5a5001e7a6679ba79112a48322510aa6bf2564","tid":1439614,"uid":132611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"